      <p style="font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; color: #444444; margin: 24px 0 0 0;">All five schools operate within the same WA16 district where Knutsford records the second-lowest crime rate in Cheshire East - a combination the Sunday Times cited when naming Knutsford among its Best Places to Live in both 2024 and 2025.</p>
