          Most WA16 residential properties pass the brine search without issues. The risk is highest within a 250-metre radius of former brine extraction points, which are concentrated in the Northwich corridor rather than Knutsford town. Buyers should obtain the CON29M search as standard practice rather than treating it as indicative of a known problem - solicitors handling WA16 transactions routinely include it in the search bundle.
        </p>

